Package: pleiodbr
Title: Read pleiodb GWAS Databases from R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Gibran", "Hemani", email = "g.hemani@bristol.ac.uk",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Self-contained reader for .pleiodb binary databases of GWAS
    z-scores. Provides PheWAS, GWAS, top-hits, block, and rho queries with
    no Python dependency. Databases are built with the Python pleiodb package.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Imports:
    zstd,
    tibble,
    dplyr,
    jsonlite
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    withr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://github.com/explodecomputer/pleiodbr
BugReports: https://github.com/explodecomputer/pleiodbr/issues
